      "writtenOn": "2019-08-28T18:29:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "btw this is not available in https://godoc.org/google.golang.org/protobuf/encoding/protojson#Marshal (and IIUC it is against the spec). We should try stop abusing it.",
